room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: We did Do Not Disturb. It was pretty tough for our second time. Brianna was a great game master though. We definitely want to do another one.

room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: Great breakout room and good service.Did as a group of seven -- three teen aged children and four parents. Was well laid out and the time definitely flied by. While we didn't complete it, we had a great time! We'll be back to try another one.

room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: Tried a room here at Breakout Games - Greenville. Had a great time! One lock was difficult to operate in Do Not Disturb. Location easy to get to. Problem free parking in the back. I LOVE that I can reserve a room just for my group! I won't do an escape room with strangers, it's just not for me. I like that the game was more than just opening locks. I can't wait to try the others!

room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: Nice establishment, friendly staff , the room ( do not disturb) was by far my favorite!! Sooo fun and spooky ! Loved it .. we also did the island room , that was pretty neat aswell ! I highly recommend this place , can't wait to try other games here

room_title: Escape room "Do Not Disturb" by Breakout Games - Greenville in Greenville
review: We did the Do Not Disturb room and even though we didn’t escape the room, we had a lot of fun! Phil was very helpful with the hints. Can’t get over how detailed the room was. I will definitely be returning.
